name: Kobar & Borah
description: The fighters of Batavia city. The Mask Fighters using their ancestor power to fight evil or became the evil itself. Kobar is for male fighters, and Borah for female fighters. Despite the Mask series will be dropped only in SOL blockchain, this special drop for Bwople x Monday Art Club Art Contest. The artwork has to be in 3 colors only: black & white + 1 solid color of your choice without using any gradient.
